  "texts": [
    "VMs see vUPMEM devices thanks to the new virtio-based specification vPIM introduces.",
    "virtio is an I/O device para-virtualization standard offering efficiency and extensibility.",
    "More details about our new specification can be found in Appendix A.1.",
    "vPIM consists of three components:• Frontend.",
    "The frontend is a virtio device driver located in the guest kernel."
  ]
}